@   ε0 = 8.8542×10⁻¹²  F/m     permittivity of free space
@   μ0 = 1.2566×10⁻⁶   H/m     permeability of free space
@   σ  = 5.6704×10⁻⁸  W/(m²K⁴) Stefan–Boltzmann constant
@   atm = 101325 Pa              standard atmosphere
@   g  = 9.80665 m/s²            standard gravity

2.99792458E8 'c_light' STO
6.6743E-11 'G' STO
6.6261E-34 'h_planck' STO
1.0546E-34 'hbar' STO
9.1094E-31 'me' STO
1.6726E-27 'mp' STO
101325 'atm' STO
9.80665 'g0' STO

